cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.DS 

This paper deals with the detection of ransomware using machine learning algorithms and pattern mining techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of data mining techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper involves the development of a system for detecting ransomware, which suggests that it could belong to cs.SE (Software Engineering).
